{"title":"绿色的歌［外一首］——张家界即景","authors":["晓雪"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":12,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的歌［外一首］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——张家界即景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去只知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地上才有大树扎根；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到这里才见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岩上照样绿树成荫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千寻高峰顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有杉树撑起绿伞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百丈悬崖上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有劲松托起绿云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼竹林如海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静听松涛阵阵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"座座山峰绿得浓郁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条溪水绿得晶莹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股绿色的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送来凉爽，送来清新；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只绿色的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着每个人的心灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘星台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过层层云雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过千级台阶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气喘吁吁，大汗淋淋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我终于登上摘星台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天不见星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举手欲及蓝天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云海漂着峰尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹰在脚下盘旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵清风拂面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身飘飘欲仙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只觉阳光特别刺眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛已到太阳身边。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}